<span id="freeTextContainer13517695838942226860">Books can be attributed to &quot;Anonymous&quot; for several reasons: <br/><br/>* They are officially published under that name <br/>* They are traditional stories not attributed to a specific author <br/>* They are religious texts not generally attributed to a specific author <br/><br/>Books whose authorship is merely uncertain should be attributed to <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4699102.Unknown' title='Unknown' rel='nofollow noopener'>Unknown</a>.</span>
